{"tid":923002,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【劇迷惡夢】Netflix宣佈停拍《漫威夜魔俠》","createTime":"2018-12-01T01:04:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-03T05:23:32.000Z","uid":130626,"like":5,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"31a653e70568e80358bea38c1a3b395437ef4a04","tid":923002,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T01:04:38.000Z","msg":"Netflix王牌英雄劇《漫威夜魔俠》（Marvel&rsquo;s Daredevil）宣佈停拍！劇集改編自Marvel漫畫，曾一度係Netflix拓展英雄劇集嘅重點項目，第一季亦非常受歡迎，但未知係咪因爲剛推出嘅第三季收視大跌，令Netflix狠心取消劇集。另外有網民發表陰謀論，指有可能迪士尼想買返夜魔俠版權自己拍，所以先令Netflix要中止節目。其實之前電視台已經取消咗《漫威盧克凱奇》（Marvel&rsquo;s Luke Cage）同《漫威鐵拳俠》（Marvel&rsquo;s Iron Fist），到現時只剩《漫威潔西卡瓊斯》（Marvel&rsquo;s Jessica Jones）與《制裁者》（The Punisher），但睇嚟都命不久矣。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181130/large/1543578179_6072.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181130%2Flarge%2F1543578179_6072.jpg&h=7fa05dab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20181201/58978031\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181201%2F58978031&d=1puHGPAGbSmSENI0cD9hRkbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=c3ee92c9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181201%2F58978031&h=b5f15970\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20181201/58978031</a>"},{"pid":"916d41b1a21ca0b096beeb051f2ac29938af1c23","tid":923002,"uid":33408,"like":1,"dislike":10,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T01:53:07.000Z","msg":"原來Iron Fist都停埋 <br />\n佢新一季唔錯嫁喎"},{"pid":"6735bfd81b5451911ea6703f811eafa72eb1524f","tid":923002,"uid":38738,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"916d41b1a21ca0b096beeb051f2ac29938af1c23","tid":923002,"uid":33408,"like":1,"dislike":10,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T0